A||H(s)||\sin(\omega t+\angle H(s))
\frac{AH(s) e^{j\omega t}-(AH(s))^{*}e^{-j\omega t} }{2j}
A
\angle(H(s))=\theta(s)
H(s)=|H(s)|e^{i\theta(s)}
\sin\bigl(\omega t+\theta(s)\bigr)={e^{i(\omega t+\theta(s))}-e^{-i(\omega t+\theta(s))}\over 2i}\ ,
A\ |H(s)|\sin\bigl(\omega t+\theta(s)\bigr)={A H(s)e^{i\omega t}-(AH(s)^* e^{-i\omega t} \over 2i}\ .
